OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill see showers or longer spells of
OL,7,Frain, heavy at times with snow hills.
OL,8,FClear periods overnight with showers
OL,9,Fmostly dying out. A cold night with
OL,10,Fsome frost.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FMainly dry with some sunshine
OL,13,Fin the morning, isolated showers along
OL,14,Fthe west coast. Dry but cloudier in
OL,15,Fthe afternoon. Patchy rain and
OL,16,Fstrengthening winds extending
OL,17,Fnortheast in the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
