OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FMainly
OL,6,Fdry with sunny intervals and just a
OL,7,Ffew showers on Saturday, these mainly
OL,8,Fin the west. More in the way of
OL,9,Fshowers on Sunday and Monday.
